c: 42
v: 13
t: "Yena Umisele kwinkolo yenu oko Wakuyalela uNûh noko Sikutyhile kuwe (Muhammad), noko Sakuyalela kuIbrâhîm noMûsâ no’Isâ ukumisela inkolo, hayi ukwenza iyantlukwano kuyo. Okunzima kwabo bayamanisa abanye kuAllâh koko ubamemela kuko. uAllâh Uzikhethela lowo Athande ukuzikhethela yena, Akhokelele kuYe lowo ubuyela kuYe (ngenguquko)"